    <title>wordpress网站搭建教程, 申请免费ssl证书let&#39;sencrypt</title>
    <url>/2020/11/29/wordpress/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>对照着视频输入参考笔记，祝你网站搭建成功</p>
<p>将域名dns解析到vps上，ssh连接进入vps</p>
<p>使用的vps是ubuntu<br><a id="more"></a></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>1.安装web软件nginx</strong></p>
<p><strong>2.</strong><br><code>sudo apt-get install nginx -y</code></p>
<p><strong>3.安装mysql数据库</strong></p>
<p>浏览器访问官网下载: <a href="https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/repo/apt/">https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/repo/apt/</a></p>
<p>下载选项中右键复制下载链接</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -OL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;repo.mysql.com&#x2F;&#x2F;mysql-apt-config_0.8.16-1_all.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>curl -OL 后面换成最新的链接<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg -i mysql-apt-config_0.8.16-1_all.deb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>sudo dpkg -i 后面换成最新的链接文件</p>
<p>出现的界面 选择ok</p>
<p>更新</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>开始安装mysql数据库</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install mysql-server -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>出现的界面 输入mysql密码</p>
<p>选择第二个 MySQL 5.X</p>
<p><strong>4.显示mysql运行状态，绿色正常</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl status mysql.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong>5.安装php</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install php -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>显示php版本</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">php -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>6.卸载apache2</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service apache2 stop</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get --purge remove apache2 -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get --purge remove apache2.2-common</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get autoremove -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>删除apache2文件夹<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &#x2F;etc</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br><span class="line">sudo rm -rf apache2</span><br><span class="line">cd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><strong>7.安装php执行脚本，7.4换成你的php版本</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install php7.4-mysql php7.4-fpm -y</span><br><span class="line">vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;php&#x2F;7.4&#x2F;fpm&#x2F;php.ini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>按 /fix_pathinfo 回车键 n键<br>按 i 键进入输入状态 删除; 1改为0<br>按 esc 键 :键 wq 回车键 保存更改退出</p>
<p>重新启动fpm<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service php7.4-fpm restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong>8.将wordpress安装包放到www里面</strong></p>
<p>wordpress官网 <a href="https://cn.wordpress.org">https://cn.wordpress.org</a></p>
<p>电脑启动ubuntu系统工具</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scp -r &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;c&#x2F;wordpress-5.4.2-zh_CN.zip root@8.8.8.8:&#x2F;var&#x2F;www</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>输入vps密码</p>
<p><strong>9.vps下载解压缩unzip</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install unzip -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><strong>10.进入www文件夹将wordpress解压缩</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &#x2F;var&#x2F;www</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br><span class="line">sudo unzip wordpress-5.4.2-zh_CN.zip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong>11.网站根目录文件夹增加权限</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo chown -R www-data:www-data &#x2F;var&#x2F;www&#x2F;wordpress</span><br><span class="line">cd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong>12.创建网站数据库</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -u root -p</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>输入mysql密码</p>
<p>创建数据库名称</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create database aaaaaa;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>创建数据库用户以及密码<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create user &#39;bbbbbb&#39;@&#39;%&#39; identified by &#39;cccccc&#39;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>授权用户<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">grant all privileges on aaaaaa.* to &#39;bbbbbb&#39;@&#39;%&#39; with grant option;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>刷新<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">flush privileges;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>退出mysql<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">quit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>重新启动mysql<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service mysql restart</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><strong>13.编辑nginx配置文件</strong><br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim &#x2F;etc&#x2F;nginx&#x2F;sites-available&#x2F;default</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>按 i 进入输入状态<br>编辑网站根文件夹 var/www/html 改为var/www/wordpress<br>添加 index.php<br>找到 server_name 输入自己的域名</p>
<p>找到<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">location &#x2F; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        添加#注释掉       # try_files $uri $uri&#x2F; &#x3D;404; </span><br><span class="line">        添加新的   try_files $uri $uri&#x2F; &#x2F;index.php?$query_string;</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>添加块，php7.4换成自己的php版本</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">location ~ \.php$ &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                try_files $uri &#x2F;index.php &#x3D;404;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_split_path_info ^(.+\.php)(&#x2F;.+)$;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_pass unix:&#x2F;var&#x2F;run&#x2F;php&#x2F;php7.4-fpm.sock;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_index index.php;</span><br><span class="line">                fastcgi_param SCRIPT_FILENAME $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;</span><br><span class="line">                include fastcgi_params;          </span><br><span class="line">                  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>继续添加块</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">location ~ \.user\.ini$ &#123;</span><br><span class="line">             deny all;</span><br><span class="line">                        &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>保存退出</p>
<p>esc : wq 回车键</p>
<p>检查nginx是否配置正确</p>
<p><code>nginx -t</code></p>
<p>显示 syntax is ok 为配置正确</p>
<p>安装php扩展</p>
<p><code>sudo apt install php7.4-gd php7.4-mbstring php7.4-xmlrpc -y</code></p>
<p>重新启动nginx<br><code>service nginx restart</code></p>
<p>打开浏览器输入网址安装wordpress</p>
<p>安装完成后，在vps中<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd &#x2F;var&#x2F;www&#x2F;wordpress     </span><br><span class="line">ls  </span><br><span class="line">vim wp-config.php</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<blockquote>
<p>数据库整理类型。如不确定请勿更改<br>define( ‘DB_COLLATE’, ” ); 下面添加</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">define(&#39;FS_METHOD&#39;,&#39;direct&#39;);</span><br><span class="line">define(&#39;FS_CHMOD_DIR&#39;,0777);</span><br><span class="line">define(&#39;FS_CHMOD_FILE&#39;,0777);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>保存退出 esc : wq 回车键<br><code>cd</code></p>
<p>网站启用https<br>申请免费ssl证书的工具网站<br><a href="https://certbot.eff.org/">https://certbot.eff.org/</a></p>
<p><code>vim /etc/nginx/sites-available/default</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server &#123;</span><br><span class="line">         listen 80 default_server;</span><br><span class="line">         listen [::]:80 default_server;</span><br><span class="line">         server_name abc0123456789.xyz www.abc0123456789.xyz;</span><br><span class="line">         return 301 https:&#x2F;&#x2F;abc0123456789.xyz$request_uri;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>域名换成自己的</p>
<p>ssl证书跟密钥</p>
<p><code>ssl_certificate 证书路径;</code><br><code>ssl_certificate_key 密钥路径;</code></p>
<blockquote>
<p>不要忘记分号</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
